title: Gomes helps Royals beat White Sox 6-4 (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 53,993 Gomes helps Royals beat White Sox 6-4 (Yahoo Sports) CHICAGO (AP) -- Jonny Gomes drove in three runs, and the banged-up Kansas City Royals moved into a tie with Toronto for the AL's best record with a 6-4 victory over the Chicago White Sox on Thursday night.
